{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/gatsby-updates","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A few more changes building on top of <a href=\"/now-powered-by-gatsby\">my previous post</a>.</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2 id=\"better-search\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#better-search\" aria-label=\"better search permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Better Search</h2>\n<p>Searching is now a partial search instead of a sub-string search</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 758px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c14876b8c84f54ea31a393b729331b7d/d5719/search.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.131455399061025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"search\"\n        title=\"search\"\n        src=\"/static/c14876b8c84f54ea31a393b729331b7d/d5719/search.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c14876b8c84f54ea31a393b729331b7d/53f68/search.png 213w,\n/static/c14876b8c84f54ea31a393b729331b7d/df70d/search.png 425w,\n/static/c14876b8c84f54ea31a393b729331b7d/d5719/search.png 758w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"comment-system\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#comment-system\" aria-label=\"comment system permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Comment System</h2>\n<p>I've moved off <a href=\"https://disqus.com/\">Disqus</a> over to <a href=\"https://github.com/umputun/remark42\">Remark42</a>. This is to be more privacy friendly.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 784px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fd0b4b4110b68f2c90d19758da79bbea/c852c/remark42.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.62910798122066%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"remark42\"\n        title=\"remark42\"\n        src=\"/static/fd0b4b4110b68f2c90d19758da79bbea/c852c/remark42.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd0b4b4110b68f2c90d19758da79bbea/53f68/remark42.png 213w,\n/static/fd0b4b4110b68f2c90d19758da79bbea/df70d/remark42.png 425w,\n/static/fd0b4b4110b68f2c90d19758da79bbea/c852c/remark42.png 784w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 784px) 100vw, 784px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"serve-fonts-locally\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#serve-fonts-locally\" aria-label=\"serve fonts locally permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serve Fonts Locally</h2>\n<p>Another change to be more privacy friendly. <a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto\">Google's Roboto font</a> is now being served from this website.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 850px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/7bc11/roboto.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.502347417840376%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"roboto\"\n        title=\"roboto\"\n        src=\"/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/d6170/roboto.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/53f68/roboto.png 213w,\n/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/df70d/roboto.png 425w,\n/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/d6170/roboto.png 850w,\n/static/c528011b239bb52f497f79e7fb092f1e/7bc11/roboto.png 878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"use-netlify-for-builds\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#use-netlify-for-builds\" aria-label=\"use netlify for builds permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use Netlify for Builds</h2>\n<p>Netlify can also build this website in addition to serving it on their CDN. This removes the need to use Gatsby Cloud which had little benefit besides the Lighthouse Auditing.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 850px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/2324c/netlify.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.154929577464785%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"netlify\"\n        title=\"netlify\"\n        src=\"/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/d6170/netlify.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/53f68/netlify.png 213w,\n/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/df70d/netlify.png 425w,\n/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/d6170/netlify.png 850w,\n/static/6c4ddbf4ed0bb8f9fe3b3b14cb1a5061/2324c/netlify.png 1229w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"delete-cloudflare\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#delete-cloudflare\" aria-label=\"delete cloudflare permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Delete Cloudflare</h2>\n<p>Another privacy change. Proxying through Cloudflare gave me a TLS/SSL certificate but also meant Cloudflare was injecting it's own analytics into each page.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 850px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/06fb1/cloudflare.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 5.633802816901409%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAIAAABR8BlyAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAARUlEQVQI12MI1NRwERbylBR3lZb0kJNxlJKwEhG2kZSwkZGykZG2kZEyFRI0FRY04eMx5eHW42Q35uezEBOxk5MxFuADAA+CCBwn6y5NAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cloudflare\"\n        title=\"cloudflare\"\n        src=\"/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/d6170/cloudflare.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/53f68/cloudflare.png 213w,\n/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/df70d/cloudflare.png 425w,\n/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/d6170/cloudflare.png 850w,\n/static/c7b8cd1291fada22a1714d701d2ea996/06fb1/cloudflare.png 1153w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To combat this I switched my DNS and cert over to Netlify. Netlify already builds the site (above) and it's CDN is more or less the same as proxying through Cloudflare. Netlify is also able to provide a cert through Let's Encrypt once I changed my DNS Nameservers over to them.</p>","timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"A few more changes building on top of my previous post. Better Search Searching is now a partial search instead of a sub-string search…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/calvin.me/calvin.me/master/posts/2020/2020-06-28-gatsby-updates/index.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Blog Updates","categories":["Blog"],"tags":["gatsby"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/bf4e9b56aa5701e2652f5b9a3c0a1237/ccc8a/thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/bf4e9b56aa5701e2652f5b9a3c0a1237/ccc8a/thumbnail.png 150w,\n/static/bf4e9b56aa5701e2652f5b9a3c0a1237/67d4a/thumbnail.png 300w","sizes":"150px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/bf4e9b56aa5701e2652f5b9a3c0a1237/3554d/thumbnail.webp 150w,\n/static/bf4e9b56aa5701e2652f5b9a3c0a1237/c437f/thumbnail.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"150px"}]},"width":150,"height":150}}}}}},"pageContext":{"filter":"/^.*\\/\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}-gatsby-updates\\/.*$/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}